# ============================================
# NOTES FOR DEPLOYMENT
# ============================================
# 1. Upload this file as ".htaccess" to your web root directory
# 2. Ensure mod_rewrite is enabled on your Apache server
# 3. Test all URLs after deployment to ensure clean URLs work
# 4. Update the FORCE WWW/NON-WWW section based on your preference
# 5. Uncomment HTTPS redirect only after SSL certificate is installed
# 6. Adjust Content-Security-Policy if you add external scripts/resources

# ============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================
# If you get 500 Internal Server Error:
# 1. Check if mod_rewrite is enabled: sudo a2enmod rewrite
# 2. Check Apache error logs: /var/log/apache2/error.log
# 3. Verify AllowOverride is set to "All" in Apache config
# 4. Comment out sections one by one to identify the issue
